# Architecture

Business logic must never live inside:

- page.tsx
- layout.tsx
- UI components

# Data Flow

API
↓
Service Layer
↓
React Query Hook
↓
Feature Component
↓
UI Component

# Never

- Call fetch directly inside components
- Call axios directly inside components
- Put API logic in UI
- Share state between features

# Always

- Use service functions
- Use query hooks
- Use feature folders
- Keep components presentational

# State

Use React Query for:

- server state
- caching
- mutations

Use Zustand only for:

- UI preferences
- temporary client state

Never store server state in Zustand.